they'll probably get all

15:37.804 --> 15:39.637
the good programs back
in school.

15:39.772 --> 15:41.638
-Perfect.
-Have you heard?

15:41.674 --> 15:45.042
The fund-raiser's being hosted
this year by all Persians.

15:45.111 --> 15:48.045
It's a completely
Persian-run event. (scoffs)

15:48.180 --> 15:50.114
Mmm.

15:52.135 --> 15:54.802
