if I can find a juice box.

15:54.871 --> 15:57.004
What's wrong?

15:57.040 --> 15:58.873
Nothing.

15:59.008 --> 16:00.941
My mom is being
so fucking weird.

16:00.944 --> 16:02.743
(scoffs) Tell me about it.

16:02.779 --> 16:04.945
My mom can't go two seconds
without me.

16:04.948 --> 16:07.548
I'm like,
just figure it out, dude.

16:07.683 --> 16:08.899
DiGIORNO (over P.A.):
Good evening, McIntosh parents.

16:09.035 --> 16:11.969
The classrooms are open,
so let the experiments begin.

16:12.104 --> 16:15.038
